stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Uploaded: Customer uploads prescription image
    
    Uploaded --> Processing: OCR job triggered
    note right of Processing
        Tesseract.js processes image
        Extracts medicine names, dosage
        Accuracy: 70-85%
    end note
    
    Processing --> Pending: OCR complete
    Processing --> Failed: OCR error
    
    Pending --> UnderReview: Pharmacist opens
    note right of Pending
        Status: Awaiting pharmacist review
        Extracted text visible
    end note
    
    UnderReview --> Verified: Pharmacist approves
    UnderReview --> Rejected: Invalid prescription
    UnderReview --> Pending: Pharmacist requests more info
    
    Verified --> ReadyToDispense: Drug interaction check passed
    note right of Verified
        Status: Approved by pharmacist
        Ready for dispensing
    end note
    
    ReadyToDispense --> OnHold: Stock unavailable
    OnHold --> ReadyToDispense: Stock replenished
    
    ReadyToDispense --> Dispensing: Sale initiated
    Dispensing --> Dispensed: Sale completed
    note right of Dispensed
        Status: Medicine dispensed
        Inventory updated
        Invoice generated
    end note
    
    Dispensed --> [*]
    Rejected --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
    
    note left of Failed
        Status: OCR processing failed
        Manual entry required
    end note
    
    note left of Rejected
        Status: Prescription rejected
        Reason logged
    end note
